These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the canadian##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the owner of the turtle and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

