.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

