.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, teacher
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the teacher is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the journalist##1
3. the person driving the trike is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | teacher | journalist |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

