.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the french##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | french  | canadian | dutch   |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | cycling |

