.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, writing
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is photography and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | baking |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, romance, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | spy     | romance |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

