.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, hiking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

